headline: Coinbase's Echo Buyout: Is it Building on the Onchain Ecosystem?
summary: Coinbase's $375M Echo buyout extends its onchain ecosystem, positioning the crypto leader as an "everything exchange" for digital assets.

headline: Is It Too Late to Consider Interactive Brokers After a 50% Surge in 2025?
summary: If you’ve been following Interactive Brokers Group lately, you know this stock has been on quite a tear. Just this year, it’s surged 50.7%, building on an impressive 83.1% gain over the past twelve months. Stretch that timeline out a bit, and the story gets even more remarkable: Interactive Brokers has returned nearly 492% over the last five years. It’s not just luck. The company has continued expanding internationally, launching new services for retail and professional traders, and growing...
